Tina CLARKE, Plaintiff,
v.
ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION, Defendant. SC: 159586 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 22, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, Plaintiff having failed to submit a copy of the June 18, 2019 order and refile a copy of the pleadings as required by the June 18, 2019 order, the Clerk of the Court is hereby directed to close this file.
